result.formatted_address: 1-27 Lan Fong Rd, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Prince Dragon Dim Sum

reviews.text: Tasty dim sum freshly steamed from order. The price is very affordable given its location. The staffs here are very helpful and attentive. But do expect the tables to be quite cramped. Also, you need to pass through their food prep area in order to get to the toilet.

Prince Dragon Dim Sum with nice dim sum and friendly staffs, but their tables are too packed, and hard to stay long for a comfortable dining.
It's good that you don't have to come with a large group to enjoy different dishes, as most of their dishes are small.  You can order two or three per person but still not full.   Price here is acceptable with average of $70 per person.
However, their tables are packed and very close to next table.  And once you finished your food, waiter will clean up your table quickly and not likely to seat and rest for a moment, as they always have long queue outside

Enjoying the tasty dim sum here with fair price, like the abalone Siu Mai and "It is not Cheung Fian" (不是腸粉) is tempura prawn wrapped with rice sheet. Recommended to seat close to the window and get more sun light, will be better if they come with bilingual menu with all the choices.

Average quality.
Comfortable environment
Nice Dim sum with reasonable price.  Has English menus

result.name: 籠太子點心

reviews.text: 出餐較慢，下午5點幾去一碟春卷要等25 分鐘！蝦餃出水濕濕地似翻蒸。但總括味道唔錯，唯員工經常聚埋一堆傾計，對顧客有D忽略。價錢係銅鑼灣嚟講都算平。
即叫即蒸的點心，個別有特色的點心！水準中上，價錢也不貴，值得再試！

粵式點心，消費每人約HK$60.0。質素與服務水平好。

result.formatted_address: Ground Floor, 11 Lan Fong Rd, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Prince Dragon Dim Sum 籠太子點心專門店

reviews.text: I go to HK regularly and this is the place  I always go to and introduce to my friends all the time. Great dimsum sold in small portions so you can try out a variety of plates. Staff do not speak English fluently but try to be helpful. Try out all the recommended dishes and you will not regret. The signature sauce that goes with the dimsum very well has become so popular that the owner now sells it in bottles. Great price as well.
Delicioussss!!! Best dim sum in causeway bay area
So good!

주문한 딤섬 모두 맛있었어요.
한국인 입맛에 딱 맞습니다.
